title: Couple With Heart Man Man Medium Dark Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone
description: Represents a romantic couple composed of two men, with specified medium-dark and medium skin tones. It signifies love, partnership, and equality for same-sex relationships.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this couple emoji portrays two men with a medium-dark and medium skin tone, connected by a vibrant, glossy red heart that seems to emanate warmth. The smooth gradients and soft highlights on their figures, along with the tender, supportive gestures, clearly convey love, partnership, and deep affection within Apple’s signature expressive style.
